        "title": "Add a heuristic to scale even single-char text, when the horizontal/vertical scaling differs significantly (issue 11713)",
        "user": {
            "login": "Snuffleupagus",
            "id": 2692120,
            "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjI2OTIxMjA=",
